cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with computer vision algorithms for 3D shape reconstruction from 2D landmark points on a single image. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) as the authors use a deep neural network algorithm. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as the algorithm is trained to learn from data. The use of data augmentation and robustness to noise and missing data suggests that the paper may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
